Hey Everyone my name is Jennifer and I'm only 20 years old. I wasn't even thought of when the war was going on and I don't know anyone who fought in it.  Right now I'm taking a history class in college about Vietnam.  I'm reading a book called WE WERE SOLDIERS...ONCE AND YOUNG.  IA DRANG THE BATTLE THAT CHANGED THE WAR IN VIETNAM.  By Lt.Gen.Harold G. Moore and Joseph L. Galloway.  I reccommend it.  It is very good and very heartbreaking. Bye  
